      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone prioritizing mechanical reliability over a perfect appearance. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dings on the passenger side, and some fading on the clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate wear and some staining consistent with regular use. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, though it may eventually benefit from routine maintenance items like new brake pads or tires in the coming year. It is a solid, honest daily driver for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a reasonable price.",
