      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s a total gem. This beauty is in pristine, showroom condition\u2014it\u2019s been pampered since day one and still looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve kept it meticulously clean, so you\u2019re getting a ride that\u2019s as close to perfect as it gets. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
