      "description": "Available for the discerning collector is an investment-grade E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving power plant utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to achieve a stratospheric 8,400 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring exceptional mechanical grip. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with documented preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The chassis is factory-spec with no subframe fatigue, and the exterior retains its original depth and luster. An uncompromising example for those seeking peak BMW M-division engineering in its most visceral form.",
